documents.name: Privacy Policy
documents.text:
Who we are

Our website address is: https://choiceofyourlife.com.

What personal data we collect and why we collect it

We make every attempt to not-collect any data about you. Backups are created for the content of this site, only. However, since we don’t enable comments or logins, there is no other data about you to collect.

The only exception are security tools we have in place. When malicious users attempt to gain unauthorized access to our system, those IP addresses are tracked so that repeat offenders can be banned.
